videos.description: Off the steal, Tony Jackson Jr. goes behind-the-back on his pass to Darin Green Jr. for a slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Behind-the-back pass sets up Green for dunk) 2020/2/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Behind-the-back pass sets up Green for dunk

videos.description: Tony Johnson Jr.'s lay-in gives Cincinnati the 70-68 lead over UCF.  A big block follows from Jarron Cumberland on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson throws up go-ahead basket for Cincy) 2020/2/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson throws up go-ahead basket for Cincy

videos.description: Cincy spreads the ball around the perimeter, ending in a Jaevin Cumberland 3-pointer to send the game to another overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jaevin Cumberland's big 3 sends game to 2OT) 2020/2/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaevin Cumberland's big 3 sends game to 2OT
